{"tid":1708652,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［冰魔法］新技能解鎖","createTime":"2019-11-11T15:50:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T00:40:36.000Z","uid":185791,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"7e624c5d72f1666feb25abda723db23338d8d779","tid":1708652,"uid":185791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T15:50:20.000Z","msg":"冰魔法<br />\n<br />\n教學<br />\n乾冰+水+汽水樽(流線型&rarr;成功率up)  &rarr;巨響<br />\n<br />\n冰魔法+鐵釘&rarr;飛釘彈 (遠離手足使用！)<br />\n<br />\n步驟<br />\n放入少量乾冰，然後加水( 會有大量白色煙霧)，快速扭實樽蓋，拋去曱甴嘅方向， 然後就等佢膨脹、爆炸。<br />\n<br />\n局限 <br />\n乾冰儲存麻煩 (需密封)<br />\n控制爆炸時間要經驗(非即爆)<br />\n最好搵甜品店入貨(難散買)<br />\n<br />\n攻略:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/CdK3jx-H3Vs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FCdK3jx-H3Vs&d=KwnMNtvToZrWMgCiTfGJQScuUNiPSPuqsSoNSJcc%2FI4%3D&h=d03c5f87\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/CdK3jx-H3Vs</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/MjbJ83-kzys\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMjbJ83-kzys&d=KwnMNtvToZrWMgCiTfGJQScuUNiPSPuqsSoNSJcc%2FI4%3D&h=c5ef471e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/MjbJ83-kzys</a><br />\n<br />\n純學術討論"},{"pid":"b849974b1227bac4a3728355e6c5b2aa6f70ae26","tid":1708652,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T15:51:19.000Z","msg":"［全民罷工妙計］繁忙時間要引狗衝入港鐵站向返工人士施襲<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1708303\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1708303</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a47af03a34f3651e340ca1ffd945cb2002ca753b","tid":1708652,"uid":307329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T15:58:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3577a1e5d3d4d7b6934b5067f438d8e9c0759e83","tid":1708652,"uid":246230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T16:00:33.000Z","msg":"let it go let it go<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85970a70bf73aaa2d02b4c5a876e8165e19c8e72","tid":1708652,"uid":185791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco